column4: Martinp23 here. Christel Dahlskjaer, the female force behind freenode, is on tough times. An old back injury got her addicted to  pharmaceutical pain pills, and now without her daily dosage of oxycontin, she will go through nasty junk sickness, and eventually die. Donate £10 or more today. For just £10, Christel can stay doped up for 3 hours. All donators will get a /pdpc/pillhead cloak. Join #freenode to donate today!  dfnwe piglit Abhijit ruan din lixinfis
